data.description: Talk about location!!  Not many properties like this one come up for sale very often in our community!..  Stately, well appointed ONE LEVEL brick home on a premier 2.36? acre lot minutes from town yet feel like you live in a private park like setting! Circa 1954 construction.  Recently updated.  total of 4 bedrooms all with on suite baths, 4.5 baths, tall ceilings, wood floors, stunning mahogany paneled den w/ fireplace, expansive sun-room w/ fp opening to a covered pergola, owners suite features a huge walk in closet/room!! elegant bath, 2 additional  guest suites, another guest suite off the opposite end of the house with handicapped assessable equipment, large formal living room with antique mantel over the 3rd fireplace, elegance and thoughtful renovations make this  home a very special place. Extra amenities are the fenced yard, sweeping paved drive with ample parking, dog kennels, storage room over the workshop area.  There is also a huge attic that could be finished for additional space. Easy to show on short notice but Must have appt. Call or text  Mimi Richards-706-506-9634to set up....
